The paper deals with the estimation and mitigation of non-reciprocity in wireless channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The proposed methods involve iterative estimation and precoding techniques, which are related to control systems (cs.SY) and multimedia systems (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper presents numerical results and comparisons, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG).
